title: Thief.Update.v1.1.incl.DLC-RELOADED
description:
Thief Update v1.1 incl DLC-RELOADED

RELOADED has released the newest updated of Thief for PC. This releases updates your game to v1.1 (build 4110.1). A list of updates is included within the pack.

The following DLCs are also unlocked:
The Bank Heist
The Predator Booster Pack
The Opportunist Booster Pack
The Ghost Booster Pack
The Moira Asylum Challenge
